description:
Karl Gustav Kempf was an Admiral of the http://anidb.net/ch1534 [Galactic Empire]. He was born in 762 UC and died in 798 UC at the Eighth Battle of http://anidb.net/ch1762 [Iserlohn]. As punishment for being defeated, he was posthumously promoted only one rank instead of the customary two ranks.
Source: Gineipaedia
name: Karl Gustav Kempf
